name: Skyracing, revisited
description:
A for left; D for right;W for accel, S for brake

(arrow keys can also be used)

After an otherwise-promising Unity project unexpectedly took more to compile than it should have (10GB of VM to compile a web game??), I looked to the freshly-released Godot 4 to re-implement the thing.

This may need to be recompiled in Mac-space in order to run in Safari
